Package: proxydriver
Version: 1.44
Section: gnome
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: network-manager
Installed-Size: 5120
Maintainer: Julien Blitte <julien.blitte@gmail.com>
Description: sets GNOME proxy settings using wifi NetworkManager profile name
 Proxydriver is little application wich handles GNOME proxy settings using
 Network Manager's data.
 Each wifi connection triggers a reconfiguration of GNOME proxy, based on
 network profile name.
